 I have had ample opportunity to evaluate her potential to succeed in graduate
 school and to become a productive scientist.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ann helped design and conduct a study of the effects of willow height on
 seed rain during her work with us in Yellowstone, an important piece of
 the story of effects of the restoration of wolves on ecosystem processes.
